  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Poster</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1946 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster announces the feature film ‘Visul unei nopţi de iarnă’ (Dream of a winter’s eve) and features a man and a woman. The dark-haired woman is wearing a dark round hat, a dark coat and a scarf. The dark-haired man is wearing a dark jacket, a light-coloured shirt and a necktie. He is looking at her, while she is looking away.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was directed by Jean Georgescu and released in 1946.</ab>
